<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{companyName}}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 15px 25px; background: #28a745; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; margin: 10px 5px; font-weight: bold; transition: background 0.3s; }
        .btn:hover { background: #218838; }
        .btn.secondary { background: #6c757d; }
        .btn.secondary:hover { background: #5a6268; }
        .feature { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; }
        .feature h4 { margin-top: 0; color: #28a745; }
        .feature p { margin-bottom: 0; }
        .tip-box { background: #fff3cd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; }
        .tip-box h4 { margin-top: 0; color: #856404; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎉 Account Verified Successfully!</h1>
            <p>Welcome to the SafishaHub family</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Congratulations {{firstName}}! 🎊</h2>
            <p>Your email has been verified and your <strong>{{role}}</strong> account is now active!</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="btn">🚀 Login to Your Account</a>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn secondary">📊 Go to Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            
            <h3>🌟 What you can do now:</h3>
            
            {{#if (eq role "Customer")}}
            <div class="feature">
                <h4>🔍 Find & Book Services</h4>
                <p>Browse and book professional car wash services in your area with just a few clicks.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h4>📅 Manage Your Bookings</h4>
                <p>Track your appointments, view service history, and manage upcoming bookings.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h4>⭐ Rate & Review</h4>
                <p>Share your experience and help others find the best car wash services.</p>
            </div>
            {{else}}
            <div class="feature">
                <h4>🏪 Setup Your Business</h4>
                <p>Create your service listings, set pricing, and manage your car wash business.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h4>📈 Track Performance</h4>
                <p>Monitor bookings, revenue, customer feedback, and business analytics.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h4>💰 Secure Payments</h4>
                <p>Get paid instantly with our secure payment processing system.</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="tip-box">
                <h4>💡 Pro Tip:</h4>
                <p>Complete your profile to get the most out of SafishaHub and {{#if (eq role "Service Provider")}}improve your visibility to customers{{else}}receive personalized service recommendations{{/if}}!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help getting started? We're here to help!</p>
            <p>Contact us: <a href="mailto:support@safishahub.com" style="color: #28a745;">support@safishahub.com</a></p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>